sketch.compiler.ast.core.typs

Class TypePrimitive

  • java.lang.Object
    • sketch.compiler.ast.core.typs.Type
      • sketch.compiler.ast.core.typs.TypePrimitive

  • public class TypePrimitive
extends Type
    A primitive type. This can be int, float, character, void, null, etc., depending on the specified type parameter.
    Version:
    $Id$
    Author:
